# Rule Router 🛣️

Evaluated first; delegates work to specialized rules.

---

## Dispatch Table

| Prio | Event Kind / Context |                                Match Condition                                | Delegate Rule ID          |
| :--: | :------------------: | :---------------------------------------------------------------------------: | :------------------------ |
|  0   |   Create dir/file    |           `src/frontend/components/{core,common,logical-units}/**`            | `rule-component-scaffold` |
|  1   |   Create dir/file    |           `src/frontend/frontend/**`<br><sub>(anything else)</sub>            | `rule-folder-structure`   |
|  2   |      Save file       | `*.{ts,tsx,js,jsx}` inside `src/`<br>**and** diff contains `await` in handler | `rule-state-events`       |
|  3   |      Save file       |                       `*.{ts,tsx,js,jsx}` inside `src/`                       | `rule-biome`              |
|  4   |   Create/Save file   |                      `*.stories.tsx` <br>or `*.spec.tsx`                      | `rule-test-story`         |
|  F   |      _fallback_      |                                 anything else                                 | `rule-biome`              |

---

## Routing Logic (concept)

```ts
function route(ev) {
  // …remaining checks per table above
}
```
